---

<div class="hero-container">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="badge-container">
      <BadgeSE>Ingeniero de Software</BadgeSE>
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-name">Alan Olvera</h1>
    <p class="hero-description">
      <strong class="hero-strong">Ingeniero de Software Mexicano</strong> con m치s de 1 a침o
